The Inventory Locations label type accepts these attributes: 
- Company
- Inventory Site
- Label Type
- Location
- Resulting Label Template

The Par Locations label type accepts these attributes:
- Company
- Item
- Label Type
- Location
- Manufacturer
- Purchase Item Group
- Resulting Label Template

The Locations label type accepts these attributes:
- Company
- Inventory Site
- Label Type
- Location
- Location Usage
- Resulting Label Template

The Receipts label type accepts these attributes:
- Company
- Deliver-To
- Delivery Type
- Do Not Print
- Include Blank Delivery Type
- Integration System
- Item
- Label Printing Unit of Measure
- Label Type
- Manufacturer
- Purchase Item Group
- Purchase Order Type
- Resulting Label Template
- Unit of Measure
- Ship-To Address
- Spend Category
- Supplier

The Goods Delivery Groups label type accepts these attributes:
- Label Type
- Resulting Label Template

The Goods Delivery Tickets label type accepts these attributes: 
- Label Type
- Resulting Label Template
Select a Par Location. The Par Locations label type doesn't accept storage locations.
